00:08.830 --> 00:10.250
你这次会说孩子的父亲是谁？
Who would you say is the father?

00:10.670 --> 00:11.750
你
You.

00:12.790 --> 00:15.290
我会让你怀上一个小王子
I'm going to put a prince in your belly.

00:17.580 --> 00:21.040
女王陛下一向赏罚分明
Our queen has a keen sense of poetic justice.

00:21.120 --> 00:22.540
如果有人能帮她除掉
What would she do for the man

00:22.630 --> 00:24.750
叛国的弟弟们她会如何回报呢？
who rids her of her treasonous brothers?

00:25.630 --> 00:28.120
我的名字……我真正的名字……
My name... my real name...

00:28.790 --> 00:30.250
是伊耿·坦格利安
is Aegon Targaryen.

00:30.920 --> 00:32.000
是真的 丹妮
It's true, Dany.

00:32.500 --> 00:33.670
如果这是真的……
If it were true...

00:34.290 --> 00:36.000
你生来就有铁王座的继承权
you'd have a claim to the Iron Throne.

00:36.460 --> 00:38.460
她不喜欢你的女王 对吧？
She doesn't like your queen, does she?

00:38.880 --> 00:40.500
她是在保护自己的家人
She's defending our family.

00:40.790 --> 00:42.170
我也是她的家人
I'm her family, too.

00:43.710 --> 00:44.920
别忘了这一点
Don't forget that.

