We're here to say goodbye to our brothers and sisters.

05:31.250 --> 05:33.580
向我们的父母告别
To our fathers and mothers.

05:35.420 --> 05:36.540
还有我们的朋友们
To our friends.

05:38.170 --> 05:40.000
我们的男女同胞
Our fellow men and women

05:40.080 --> 05:42.710
放下了彼此间的隔阂
who set aside their differences...

05:44.120 --> 05:45.630
并肩作战
to fight together...

05:47.290 --> 05:49.790
共同牺牲
and die together

05:49.840 --> 05:53.040
<b>塔斯的布蕾妮
</b>爵士 “美人”

05:49.840 --> 05:53.040
<b>詹姆·兰尼斯特
</b>“弑君者”

05:49.880 --> 05:51.830
其他人才得以继续生存
so that others might live.

05:54.420 --> 05:56.750
这世上所有人
Everyone in this world

05:56.830 --> 05:59.630
都欠他们一份无法偿还的债
owes them a debt that can never be repaid.

06:01.080 --> 06:04.000
永远铭记他们的事迹
It is our duty and our honor

06:04.080 --> 06:07.290
是我们的责任和荣耀
to keep them alive in memory...

06:08.460 --> 06:10.170
让我们的子孙后代
for those who come after us...

06:11.380 --> 06:13.290
以及后代的后代
and those who come after them...

06:15.170 --> 06:18.170
永世不忘 直到世界尽头
for as long as men draw breath.

06:20.080 --> 06:23.580
他们是守护王国的坚盾
They were the shields that guarded the realms of men.

06:23.940 --> 06:27.360
<b>桑铎·克里冈
</b>“猎狗”

06:23.940 --> 06:27.360
<b>戴佛斯·席渥斯
</b>“洋葱骑士”

06:24.960 --> 06:27.790
他们的忠勇后无来者
And we shall never see their like again.

